node.name: Chestnut (Women's)
node.title: UGG Tasman Slipper Chestnut (Women's)
node.description:
The UGG Tasman Slipper Chestnut W has become one of the classic colorways of the Australian brand's slippers.

 This Tasman Slipper for women construction features a combination of a foam footbed and Tread-lite outsole that is meant to provide a long-lasting fabrication. The UGG branding logo appears on the slipper’s upper. The Chestnut colored UGGs also feature the Tasman braid that is embroidered along its lining. To complete the design are the upcycled wool and the lyocell insole.

The UGG Tasman Slipper Chestnut W made its debut on the market in November 2021, with an original retail price of $100.

node.name: Chestnut (Women's)
node.title: UGG Classic Ultra Mini Boot Chestnut (Women's)
node.description:
The UGG Classic Ultra Mini Chestnut W, dressed in a Chestnut colorway, is a shoe for women.

The Classic Ultra Mini by Australian brand UGG features a Twinface sheepskin upper, a Suede heel counter with a rear pull tab, upcycled wool, a lyocell insole, a Foam footbed, and a Treadlite outsole. The sneaker’s design is completed by the textile binding that is made from recycled polyester fibers. The sneaker’s woven heel features a UGG labeled logo. Its outsole is trodden for traction.

The UGG Classic Ultra Mini Chestnut W was first made available on the 3rd of November, 2021. At the time, the retail price was set at $140.

node.name: Chestnut (Women's)
node.title: UGG Tazz Slipper Chestnut (Women's)
node.description:
The UGG Tazz Slipper Chestnut W for women features a heat-embossed UGG logo on its side.

This UGG model has the silhouette of UGG Slippers with a 1.5" platform sole for extra cushioning. It is made from the same suede upper as the original one in a chestnut color. It is also lined with the signature UGG plush wool blend for a slipper-like feel. Its textile binding is made from 100% recycled polyester fibers material.

The UGG Tazz Slipper Chestnut W was originally released on the 1st November 2021, with a retail price set at $120.

node.name: Chestnut
node.title: UGG Tasman Slipper Chestnut
node.description:
The UGG Tasman Slipper Chestnut has become one of the most known colorways in the catalog and is constructed with wool fabric.

It has a foam footbed with a Treadlite outsole, as well as a Tasman braid that is stitched along the interior of the shoe, finishing the look after signature branding is stamped on the upper. Moreover, the footwear is waterproof and includes a detachable UGGplushTM sock made of recycled wool and TENCELTM Lyocell. The sole has the brand´s starburst pattern for traction.

The UGG Tasman Slipper Chestnut was released on the market on November 1st, 2021, and retailed at $100.

node.name: Lightning McQueen
node.title: Crocs Classic Clog Lightning McQueen
node.description:
The Crocs Classic Clog Lightning McQueen is an official collaboration with Disney Pixar's Cars franchise. These Lightning McQueen Crocs pay homage to the movie's lead character, who is voiced by Owen Wilson. The Crocs look is loosely based on the Chevrolet Corvette C1, a racing car produced between 1953 and 1962.

These Lightning McQueen Crocs feature a red foam construction with printed graphics that resemble Lightning McQueen. Ventilation holes on the upper with a sole with grooves add the finishing touch.

The Crocs Classic Clog Lightning McQueen originally released in April of 2021 and retailed for $50, and restocked through the years with the retail price eventually increasing to $60.

Please note: the light up features on the Crocs Classic Clog Lightning McQueen's are not replaceable or rechargeable (and thus may not light up).

node.name: Black (Women's)
node.title: UGG Tasman Slipper Black (Women's)
node.description:
The UGG Tasman Slipper Black W is a suede slipper that features an embroidered trim and a plush genuine-shearling lining as well as a Treadlite sole.
​
​This Tasman Slipper for women by Australian shoe brand UGG is a slip-on model with a black suede upper. The lightweight slipper is lined with plush UGG wool for warmth. Underfoot, there is a foam footbed combined with an external Treadlite outsole for traction. For branding, a heat-embossed UGG logo appears on the lateral side.
​
​The UGG Tasman Slipper Black W was originally released on the 1st of November 2021, with its initial retail price set at $100.

node.name: Chesnut (Kids)
node.title: UGG Tasman II Slipper Chesnut (Kids)
node.description:
The UGG Tasman II Slipper Chesnut Kids is footwear sized for kids that can be worn indoors or outdoors, functioning as both a slipper and a shoe.

It features a soft suede upper in a warm chestnut brown colorway with Tasman branding around the cuff. The plush lining and insole are made of UGGpure upcycled wool. This version has a foam footbed and an outsole made from lightweight Treadlite by UGG. Polyester binding constructed from recycled polyester fiber holds the slipper together.

The UGG Tasman II Slipper Chesnut Kids was released on November 16th, 2017, at a retail price of $70.

node.name: Black
node.title: UGG Tasman Slipper Black
node.description:
The UGG Tasman Slipper Black can be worn both indoors and outdoors, functioning as either a slipper or a boot.

This Tasman Slipper model is made from soft black suede and has an embroidered with Tasman braiding circling the cuff. The lining is made from sheepskin and upcycled wool. The cushioned insole is made from UGG pure upcycled wool. The outsole, with traction fashioned in a starburst pattern, is made from black Treadlite technology. This version is monochromatic and the dominant hue is black. 

The UGG Tasman Slipper Black was first released at a price of $100 retail on November 1st, 2021.

node.name: Chestnut (Women's)
node.title: UGG Disquette Slipper Chestnut (Women's)
node.description:
The UGG Disquette Slipper Chestnut W is footwear sized for women (W) that come with plush lining and a thick outsole.

This slipper features a soft upper in a chestnut brown colorway with a rounded toe, a raised center seam, and heat-embossed UGG branding on the lateral side. This model has a sheepskin insole with a branding patch and a sheepskin collar and lining. The 1-inch platform outsole is constructed from Treadlite by UGG as well as EVA. Recycled polyester fibers bind this slipper together.

The UGG Disquette Slipper Chestnut W was released in January 2021 at a retail price of $100.

node.name: Mater
node.title: Crocs Classic Clog Mater
node.description:
The Crocs Classic Clog Mater steps into the scene with a playful spirit, mirroring the whimsy of Disney Pixar’s Cars. This funky edition is no ordinary pair; it’s a tribute to Mater, the beloved tow truck from Radiator Springs. From the front, a glossy TPU overlay showcases Mater’s grin, while the back flaunts a tow hook detail on the heel strap, making every step a statement of fun and comfort.

Mater's unique charm doesn't end there; these clogs feature an exposed engine design on the toe, a quirky touch that is bound to turn heads. The Crocs Classic Clog Mater isn’t just about looks; it’s about celebrating youthful exuberance with a comfy, snug fit that’s ready for adventure. The blend of iconic Crocs comfort with Mater's playful persona makes this pair a must-have for those looking to add a touch of whimsy to their footwear collection.

Dropped on October 17, 2023, at a retail price of $60, this pair is a ride into the playful world of Radiator Springs.

node.name: Chestnut (Women's)
node.title: UGG Classic Ultra Mini Platform Boot Chestnut (Women's)
node.description:
The UGG Classic Ultra Mini Platform Chestnut W is a women’s sized slip-on ankle boot that is available in a chestnut colorway.

This Ultra Mini Platform model by Australian shoe company UGG is a take on the 70’s version, maintaining iconic staples such as the sheep skin interior and the suede upper, as well as the color. The upgraded version gets a 2-inch platform sole on the Treadlite outsole underfoot, and the design keeps branding minimal, with only a leather patch appearing at the back.

The UGG Classic Ultra Mini Platform Chestnut W was first released on the 2nd of November 2022 and retailed for $150.
node.model: UGG Classic Ultra Mini Platform Boot

node.name: Mustard Seed (Women's)
node.title: UGG Tasman Slipper Mustard Seed (Women's)
node.description:
The UGG Tasman Slipper Mustard Seed Womens is a timeless shoe design that allows for comfort both indoors and outdoors. Made to keep your feet warm while protecting them from the elements, this slipper features the same durable rubber sole as the classic UGG boot design.

This version of the Women´s UGG Tasman slipper is a slip-on shoe lined with soft wool for extra comfort and warmth. The suede upper appears in a Mustard Seed colorway, giving it a warm and versatile look to match the feel it has on your feet. For a cozy element of style, it features Tasman braids lining the area where you slide your foot into the slipper. The UGG logo is heat-embossed into the suede of the shoe just beneath the braids.

What our StockX experts think stands out about this shoe is the durable rubber sole that allows for both indoor and outdoor wear. Because of this element, this slipper is not confined to being just an indoor shoe. The UGG Tasman Slipper Mustard Seed Womens was released on September 1st, 2023, for a retail price of $110.

node.name: Mustard Seed (Women's)
node.title: UGG Tazz Slipper Mustard Seed (Women's)
node.description:
The UGG Tazz Slipper in Mustard Seed Women’s dropped on September 1, 2023. This slipper fuses the timeless allure of UGG with a fresh twist, perfect for the modern enthusiast.

Crafted in a vibrant Mustard Seed hue, this Tazz Slipper shines with classic Tasman braiding encircling the cuff, evoking an effortless style synonymous with UGG. The spotlight, however, is on its elevated platform sole standing tall at 1.5 inches (38 mm), merging a classic design with an edgy touch.

But what's truly captivating about the Tazz design is the iconic UGG comfort paired with unmatched quality. Imagine stepping on clouds while flaunting the fashion-forward aesthetic. The UGG Tazz Slipper Mustard Seed, where comfort meets chic, was introduced on September 1, 2023, and initially graced the market at a sleek $120.

node.name: Black (Kids)
node.title: UGG Tasman II Slipper Black (Kids)
node.description:
The UGG Tasman II Slipper Black Kids is slip-on footwear sized for kids that can serve as a slipper or a shoe.

The upper section of this Tasman II Slipper is made of black suede with UGG Tasman braid detailing around the cuff. The lining and insole are made from 17 mm pure upcycled wool. The shoe also features 100% recycled polyester fiber binding and a heat-embossed logo on the upper. Composed of Treadlite technology, the lightweight outsole is for both cushioning and sunburst-pattern traction.

The UGG Tasman II Slipper Black Kids was released in January 2018 at a retail price of $70.

node.name: Heritage Braid Natural (Women's)
node.title: UGG Tazz Slipper Heritage Braid Natural (Women's)

node.name: DreamWorks Shrek
node.title: Crocs Classic Clog DreamWorks Shrek
node.description:
The Crocs Classic Clog took an adventurous turn with the DreamWorks Shrek collaboration, released on September 13, 2023. This iconic footwear got a fairytale twist, boasting details inspired by our favorite ogre.

Coming in a swamp-inspired color scheme, this clog captures the essence of Shrek, merging greens and browns harmoniously. But what truly sets it apart? The toe box showcases the unmistakable Shrek nose and ear details, injecting a playful vibe and bringing out the magic of the animated classic.

What's really cool about this Crocs x Shrek design is the signature comfort of the Classic Clog combined with the enchanting allure of DreamWorks. Whether you're headed on an adventure around town or Far Far Away, these are the perfect fit. The Crocs Classic Clog DreamWorks Shrek collab dropped on September 13, 2023, and was initially priced at a magical $60.

node.name: Chestnut (Kids)
node.title: UGG Tazz Slipper Chestnut (Kids)
node.description:
The UGG Tazz Slipper Chestnut (Kids) adopts the silhouette of its predecessor, the Tasman, but introduces bold features, including a SugarSole EVA outsole and midsole with a combined height of one inch.

A chestnut colorway adorns this UGG Tazz Slipper for kids. On the upper, this slipper clads a suede material with a plush matte finish. Across the vamp is a raised knit boundary running from the toe tip. There is an embossed UGG branding embellishing the lateral side. The collar breaks from the monochrome chestnut hue, and it introduces a colorful finish with a Tasman braid made from recycled polyester in white and dark red colors. A vibrantly colored pull tab adorns the heel counter.

What stands out in the UGG Tazz Slipper Chestnut (Kids)? We like the white, comfy lining of this slipper, made from UGGplush recycled wool. The vamp features lyocell lining, while the insole clads in wool and additional branding in red. When this slipper was released on January 25th, 2023, it retailed at $85.

node.name: Suede Taupe
node.title: Birkenstock Boston Soft Footbed Suede Taupe
node.description:
The Birkenstock Boston Soft Footbed Suede Taupe is an all-year round clog. This shoe comes in a taupe color way.

This Boston Footbed model by Birkenstock was inspired by nature and has a soft suede upper that surrounds the foot. It also includes a soft footbed with an extra integrated foam layer for cushioning. One strap with a metal pin buckle that may be adjusted is also featured on this product.

The Birkenstock Boston Soft Footbed Suede Taupe made its first entry into the market on the 31st of August, 2021, with $155 as the recommended retail price.

node.name: Black (Women's)
node.title: UGG Tazz Slipper Black (Women's)
node.description:
The UGG Tazz Slipper Black W takes on the slip-in silhouette, and retains most of the classics of the shoe brand, including the suede upper, wool lining, and the Treadlite rubber outsole.

The Tazz Slipper Black for women has a black suede upper, with a patterned multicolor collar providing the only contrast. On the inside, it features plush UGG sheepskin wool throughout the lining. The foam footbed is present in the rest of the underfoot. UGG maintains its signature Treadlite rubber outsole for traction under a 1.5-inch platform sole.

The UGG Tazz Slipper Black W was originally released on the 1st of November 2021 for an initial retail price of $120.

node.name: Chestnut (Women's)
node.title: UGG Classic Mini II Boot Chestnut (Women's)
node.description:
The UGG Classic Mini II Boot Chestnut W has become a part of the women's (W) boot collection.

Dressed in a chestnut colorway, this Classic Mini Boot features an upper constructed with water-repellant suede and a sheepskin-lined interior in a contrasting tone. A 17mm sheepskin insole complements the interior lining. Other details include a tag label on the heel with UGG branding, polyester binding, a heel pull tab, and overclock stitch detailing on joints. A Treadlite UGG sole with multidirectional treads for traction completes the design.

The UGG Classic Mini II Boot Chestnut W was released on February 1st, 2022, retailing at $150.

node.name: McDonald's Grimace
node.title: Crocs Classic Cozzzy Sandal McDonald's Grimace
node.description:
Get cozy with the McDonald's x Crocs Classic Cozzzy Sandal featuring everyone's favorite purple character, Grimace. These unique sandals lined with warm, fuzzy faux fur bring comfort and a playful vibe to your steps. The two-strap upper showcases Grimace’s loveable expression, along with a special shake-shaped Jibbitz charm, for a touch of whimsy.

Not only are these sandals fun to wear, but they also offer Crocs' iconic comfort. The style-forward heightened outsoles and Croslite foam footbeds provide lasting comfort, making these sandals perfect for casual outings or simply lounging at home. The inclusion of custom McDonald’s Grimace Jibbitz charms adds to their charm and collectibility.

Available on November 14, 2023, for $70, these Crocs Classic Cozzzy Sandals are a must-have for fans of unique and comfortable footwear. Embrace the spirit of Grimace and step into a world of coziness and fun with these exclusive sandals.

node.name: Wheat
node.title: Timberland 6" Premium Waterproof Boot Wheat
node.description:
The Timberland 6 Inch Premium Waterproof Wheat is one of the variants from the Timberland brand, a common footwear among men and trekking sports enthusiasts.

The boot is made from leather material at the upper part and rubber at the sole. The design unleashes in style code TB010062-713. 90% of the upper part of Timberland Waterproof is wheat, while the collar is black. The design consists of a stylish suede with a Timberland logo branded on the side of the shoe.

Timberland 6 Inch Premium Waterproof Wheat was first released on June 1, 2019, at a retail price of $210.

node.name: Goat (Women's)
node.title: UGG Tasman Slipper Goat (Women's)
node.description:
The UGG Tasman Slipper Goat is a slip-on shoe that became part of the collection of the American brand.

This slipper features a soft suede upper in a goat tone and a collar opening with embroidered Tasman braid. The upper is lined with UGGplush, which comprises 80% upcycled wool and 20% lyocell insole. UGGpure wool insole is also used. Other details include the UGG logo christened on the collar cap, a moccasin-style center seam, and polyester binding. Rounding out the design is a Treadlite sole for comfort.

The UGG Tasman Slipper Goat was released on November 30th, 2022, retailing at $100.

node.name: Grey (Women's)
node.title: UGG Classic Ultra Mini Boot Grey (Women's)
node.description: The UGG Classic Ultra Mini Boot Grey W is a versatile and stylish footwear option for women. Made with high-quality materials, these boots feature a soft and cozy sheepskin lining that provides warmth and comfort during colder months. The grey colorway adds a touch of sophistication to any outfit, making it perfect for both casual and formal occasions. These boots were released on StockX on an undisclosed date and are currently available for purchase at a retail price of $140. With its classic design and premium construction, the UGG Classic Ultra Mini Boot Grey W is a must-have addition to any fashion-forward wardrobe.

node.name: Antilope (Women's)
node.title: UGG Classic Ultra Mini Boot Antilope (Women's)
node.description:
The UGG Classic Ultra Mini Antilope W are women-sized ankle boots that feature a suede upper and are available in an antelope brown color.

The Ultra Mini boots by UGG are designed with a brown suede upper crafted from sheepskin. The sheepskin suede upper is lightweight, and the thick and fluffy interior is made for warmth. Underfoot, the slip-in style classic ankle boots sit on a rubber outsole that rounds off the design.

The UGG Classic Ultra Mini Antilope W was originally released on the 1st of November 2021. The retail price was set at $140.

node.name: by Salehe Bembury Sasquatch
node.title: Crocs Pollex Clog by Salehe Bembury Sasquatch
node.description:
Since its release, Crocs Pollex Clog by Salehe Bembury Sasquatch remains of the highest-selling variants in the Crocs catalog.

The construction of Pollex Clog mainly utilizes croslite material. These Crocs come in an attractive sasquatch black colorway and feature a heel attached to the optional sport mode for great fitting. The upper part is perforated to enhance its breathability and allow the shedding of water and other particles, such as debris, from inside the Crocs.

The Crocs Pollex Clog by Salehe Bembury Sasquatch was released on September 22, 2022. At the time of the release, its retail price was $85.

node.name: Black (Women's)
node.title: UGG Classic Ultra Mini Boot Black (Women's)
node.description:
The UGG Classic Ultra Mini Black W comes in an all-black color scheme. The upper of this shoe is made from soft twin-face sheepskin.

The upper of this Mini Black model for women (W) comes with 17mm sheepskin lining throughout. The UGGplush™ technology was used in crafting the insoles of this shoe. The back of this UGG Classic shoe features a black colored "UGG" printing and its textile binding is made from recycled polyester fibers.

The UGG Classic Ultra Mini Black W was released in the market on 23rd May 2022 and its retail price was $140.

node.name: Smoke Plume (Women's)
node.title: UGG Classic Ultra Mini Boot Smoke Plume (Women's)

node.name: Burnt Olive (Women's)
node.title: UGG Tasman Slipper Burnt Olive (Women's)
node.description:
The UGG Tasman Slipper Burnt Olive W is a slip-on footwear for women that can be worn as either a slipper or a shoe.

This Burnt Tasman Slipper model has an upper section made from soft suede with embroidered braiding around the cuff. The plush lining combines sheepskin and upcycled wool and the insole is made from upcycled wool. The outsole is made of Treadlite by UGG and features a starburst traction pattern. This sustainable slipper with a heat embossed logo is held together by 100% recycled polyester fiber binding.

The UGG Tasman Slipper Burnt Olive W was released on November 1st, 2021 at a retail price of $100.

node.name: Mustard Seed (Women's)
node.title: UGG Classic Ultra Mini Platform Boot Mustard Seed (Women's)
node.description:
The UGG Classic Ultra Mini Platform Boot in Mustard Seed showcases a perfect blend of the classic UGG comfort with a trendy twist. The mustard seed hue, rich suede exterior, and platform sole give it a fresh look, perfect for the fashion forward crowd that values style as much as functionality.

With the iconic plush sheepskin lining, these boots promise warmth on chilly days. Moreover, the Treadlite by UGG outsole offers traction and durability, making them a perfect fit for any adventure. The mini height adds a unique touch, standing out while ensuring your feet are snug and cozy.

Always ahead in the fashion game, this boot was released on September 1st, 2023. Priced at $150, they offer a contemporary look without compromising the classic UGG comfort.
node.model: UGG Classic Ultra Mini Platform Boot

node.name: by Salehe Bembury Niagara
node.title: Crocs Pollex Clog by Salehe Bembury Niagara
node.description:
The Crocs Pollex Clog by Salehe Bembury Niagara clog features a unique collaboration between Crocs and renowned footwear designer Salehe Bembury. The slide has a unique silhouette that is composed of three of Salehe Bembury’s signature fingerprints combined, available in the Niagara colorway.

The Niagara Salehe Bembury Crocs Pollex Clog showcases a "Niagara" color scheme, drawing inspiration from the Serene Gray tones observed at Niagara Falls. With its distinctive concave ridges, this model offers a breathable design, enhanced by intricate cut-out details, and is completed with the addition of a side strap for added functionality. The neutral color scheme is harmoniously paired with a lightweight foam construction, while the concave ridges serve as a practical water siphoning system. The adjustable heel strap proudly showcases dual branding from both Crocs and Salehe Bembury, featuring embossed logos for a distinctive touch.

What our experts love about Crocs Pollex Clog by Salehe Bembury Niagara is its unique design. This collaboration with Salehe Bembury combines elements inspired by nature with innovative design details to create a unique clog that’s not only visually striking, but also comfortable and practical. The clog debuted for $85 on July 20th, 2023.

node.name: Sand (Women's)
node.title: UGG Classic Ultra Mini Boot Sand (Women's)
node.description:
The UGG Classic Ultra Mini Boot Sand W is sized specifically for women. It can function as either a slipper or a shoe.

This Mini Boot in a Sand colorway has a Twinface sheepskin upper with a suede heel counter. The upper also features an asymmetrical top line, topical treatment for weather protection, raised seams, and a pull tab on the heel. The lining is composed of sheepskin, the insole of UGGplush upcycled wool, and the outsole of Treadlite by UGG with a sunburst traction pattern.

The UGG Classic Ultra Mini Boot Sand W was released in January 2020 at a retail price of $140.

node.name: Black Nubuck Premium
node.title: Timberland 6" Boot Black Nubuck Premium
node.description:
The Timberland 6-Inch Black Nubuck features a black Nubuck leather construction which comes from top-grain calfskin or cowhide. The leather is layered on the collar to create comfort and protect the feet from outside elements. Timberland also includes anti-fatigue technology that absorbs sudden impact and returns that energy to where it came from.

The Timberland 6-Inch Black Nubuck released in January of 2018 and retailed for $190.

node.name: Dark Grey
node.title: UGG Tasman Slipper Dark Grey
node.description:
In the UGG Tasman Slipper Dark Grey, a slip-on silhouette is embellished by an all-suede base in a dark grey hue and a buoyant sole in a slightly lighter tone.

The UGG Tasman Slipper’s upper is constructed from grey suede and is adorned by a sewn seam with visible thread, which runs from the toe tip to the collar. The menial quarter panel is an uninterrupted flow of suede, while the lateral features the UGG branding in an imprinted form. Artistic embroidery is present on the ankle cages. It spans the entire circumference of the collar and comprises polyester black and light grey threads in an intertwined pattern.

StockX experts adore the sole design employed on this slipper. It has grey all-around stitching and grey suede piping. The Eva outsole has a matching color and features the SugarSole technology by UGG for extra durability and comfort. When it was released on March 14th, 2020, the UGG Tasman Slipper Dark Grey had a retail price of $100.

node.name: Chestnut (Women's)
node.title: UGG Neumel Platform Chelsea Boot Chestnut (Women's)
node.description:
The UGG Neumel Platform Chelsea Boot Chestnut brings a fusion of the brand's iconic comfort with an elevated modern twist. Flaunting the rich chestnut shade on its luxe suede exterior, it screams sophistication and style.

The boot's design showcases a plush interior, cradling your feet with its signature sheepskin lining. Topped off with an enhanced platform and elastic side panels, it merges timeless aesthetics with urban appeal. A Treadlite by UGG outsole ensures you stay grounded, combining durability with flexibility.

Stepping onto the scene on October 19th, 2022, this fashionable boot can be yours for $150, combining UGG's enduring craftsmanship with modern design elements.
